{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It may be that we had to pay a lot of money for him to come to England.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There are all sorts of things that I've heard now, which were the rules, at that time, in Britain for-- asylum seekers is the word now and refugees.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it's very interesting to compare our situation in 1936 with what's going on today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But one way or another, my father did not come with us to London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And, and this is, again, one of these things that we never discussed with our parents-- why he didn't come.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we also didn't discuss them with our Uncle Rudi and Lotte, which, which was a great shame because they only died a couple of years ago.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, and we should have really asked them all these kind of questions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I didn't think it was important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We knew that he hadn't come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I didn't think it was important why he hadn't come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But it is now because reciting the story and writing my book about it all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I wished I did know, definitely, why he didn't come to London.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were left with Uncle Rudi and Lotte in, in London.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, actually-- and Rudi-- went to a school, the West Hampstead Day School, a Jewish school, in London.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to learn, of course, a new language because we couldn't speak any English.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we made our way there at school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we played.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I particularly admired Uncle Rudi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uncle Rudi, in many ways, was my role model.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was an intellectual and an academic and not a practical man and not a sportsman.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
